# GitHub — parthha12 only

All GitHub operations for this project use **`parthha12`** (renamed from torrap11). Do not use `parthhar` or other accounts unless the user explicitly overrides.

## Defaults

- **Owner:** `parthha12`
- **Remote:** `https://github.com/parthha12/<repo>.git`
- **CLI:** Before `gh` commands, run `gh auth switch --user torrap11` (keyring label; login is `parthha12`).
- **This repo:** `https://github.com/parthha12/proactive-recall`

## Commands

- New repos: `gh repo create parthha12/<name> ...` or `gh repo create <name> ...` while switched to torrap11.
- PRs/issues: target `parthha12/*` only.
- Never push to `parthhar/*` for this workstream.

## Spelling

GitHub username is **`parthha12`** (two h’s, one r) — not `parthhar12` or `parthhar`.
